== 正規賽 ==
左投[[羅恩·吉德里|羅恩·吉德里]]在這季成為洋基隊20世紀最後一名至少拿下25勝的投手<ref>''Great Baseball Feats, Facts and Figures'', 2008 Edition, p. 99, David Nemec and Scott Flatow, A Signet Book, Penguin Group, New York, {{ISBN|978-0-451-22363-0}}</ref>。本季含季後賽他總共先發35場，主投273⅔局拿下25勝3敗、奪三振248次、防禦率1.74，還外加9次完封，這樣優異的表現讓吉德里在[[賽揚獎|賽揚獎]]獲得全票無異議入選<ref name=reunan>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Tt0hAAAAIBAJ&pg=4453%2C687186 |work=Reading Eagle |location=(Pennsylvania) |agency=Associated Press |title=Guidry unanimous Cy Young winner |date=1978-11-01 |page=65}}</ref><ref name=susplck>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=PvZLAAAAIBAJ&pg=4991%2C754486 |work=Spokesman-Review |location=(Spokane, Washington) |agency=Associated Press |title=Suspense lacking for Ron Guidry |date=1978-11-02 |page=32}}</ref><ref name=sivyfl>{{cite magazine |url=https://vault.si.com/vault/1979/01/22/yankee-from-louisiana-ron-guidry-the-cajun-with-the-shotgun-left-arm-mowed-down-american-league-hitters-last-season-now-hes-back-home-by-the-bayou-trying-to-be-just-another-guidry |magazine=Sports Illustrated |last=Moses |first=Sam |title=Yankee from Louisiana |date=1979-01-22 |page=60 |access-date=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2020-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200828074725/https://vault.si.com/vault/1979/01/22/yankee-from-louisiana-ron-guidry-the-cajun-with-the-shotgun-left-arm-mowed-down-american-league-hitters-last-season-now-hes-back-home-by-the-bayou-trying-to-be-just-another-guidry }}</ref>。

[[救援投手|救援投手]][[戈斯·戈沙基|戈斯·戈沙基]]也以27次[[救援成功|救援成功]]拿下[[美國聯盟|美國聯盟]][[DHL年度救援王獎|年度救援王]]，並贏得[[美國職棒大聯盟年度最佳救援投手獎|年度最佳救援獎]]。

=== 賽季概述 ===
7月的[[1978年美國職棒大聯盟全明星賽|全明星賽]]結束後一周，洋基還落後當時的美聯東區龍頭[[1978年波士頓紅襪隊球季|紅襪隊]]達14場勝差，但他們隨後就在賽季後半一追趕至並列第一。在賽季還有一個禮拜時，洋基隊反倒領先一場勝差還拉出六連勝<ref name=mygfiat>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=5JczAAAAIBAJ&pg=6769%2C144515 |work=Eugene Register-Guard |location=(Oregon) |agency=wire service reports |title='Miracle' Yanks go for it all today |date=1978-10-01 |page=7B |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317093152/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=5JczAAAAIBAJ&pg=6769%2C144515 }}</ref>，但10月1日星期日最後一場在自家主場面對{{le|1978年克里夫蘭印地安人隊球季|1978 Cleveland Indians season|印地安人隊}}卻慘遭滑鐵盧，而紅襪隊則是最後八場全勝<ref name=rwgsac>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=3AZSAAAAIBAJ&pg=5513%2C192978 |work=Nashua Telegraph |location=New Hampshire |agency=UPI |last=McMane |first=Fred |title=Rick Waits gives Sox another chance |date=1978-10-02 |page=32 |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210617061810/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=3AZSAAAAIBAJ&pg=5513%2C192978 }}</ref><ref name=wmsbcy>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=SesyAAAAIBAJ&pg=6530%2C379711 |work=Wilmington Morning Star |location=North Carolina |agency=wire reports |title=Bosox catch Yanks; playoff set today |date=1978-10-02 |page=3B |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210617061821/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=SesyAAAAIBAJ&pg=6530%2C379711 }}</ref><ref name=ylabon>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=TM1eAAAAIBAJ&pg=3226%2C592352 |work=Lewiston Morning Tribune |location=Idaho |agency=Associated Press |title=Yankees lose a big one |date=1978-10-02 |page=5B |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317093157/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=TM1eAAAAIBAJ&pg=3226%2C592352 }}</ref>。洋基隊隨後來到[[芬威球場|芬威球場]]，並在[[1978年美國聯盟東區封王決勝加賽|單場決勝加賽]]中以5比4擊敗紅襪隊，成功在美聯東區封王；這場周一下午的比賽中，最讓人為之一亮的，乃是以擅打擊著名的{{le|巴基·登特|Bucky Dent}}竟在七局上半打出驚天一擊的三分全壘打，隨後[[瑞吉·傑克森_(棒球運動員)|瑞吉·傑克森]]在八局上擊出的陽春全壘打更是成了這場比賽的關鍵分<ref name=ywpogth/><ref name=yedbsxptn/><ref name=ydrsprfp/>。

數十年來，部分人誤以為洋基隊是從落後14½場勝差迎頭趕上，但實際上他們最多只落後14場勝差（7月17日輸球至7月20日贏球的這段時間）<ref name=stjul18>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=QMhYAAAAIBAJ&pg=6567%2C4979634 |work=Eugene Register-Guard |location=(Oregon) |title=How they stand |date=1978-07-18 |page=4C |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317092943/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=QMhYAAAAIBAJ&pg=6567%2C4979634 }}</ref><ref name=bbsal>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=CfZLAAAAIBAJ&pg=6941%2C1482207 |work=Spokesman-Review |location=Spokane, Washington |title=Baseball standings: American League |date=1978-07-19 |page=18 |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210617061814/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=CfZLAAAAIBAJ&pg=6941%2C1482207 }}</ref>。洋基隊在9月16日打敗紅襪隊之後，來到本季最大的領先，達3½場勝差<ref name=slpmcky>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=xflVAAAAIBAJ&pg=6650%2C4941841 |work=Eugene Register-Guard |location=Oregon |agency=wire service reports |title=Yankees slip a 'Mickey' past Yaz |date=1978-09-17 |page=8B}}</ref><ref name=reupfl>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ppFVAAAAIBAJ&pg=4896%2C4002021 |work=Reading Eagle |location=Pennsylvania |agency=UPI |title=Yankees fly to 3½-game lead |date=1978-09-17 |page=85 |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317093114/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ppFVAAAAIBAJ&pg=4896%2C4002021 }}</ref>洋基隊在前一個周末四連戰橫掃了紅襪隊，被體育媒體稱作「[[波士頓大屠殺|波士頓大屠殺]]」<ref name=sivsabelv>{{cite magazine |url=https://vault.si.com/vault/1978/09/25/seeing-aint-believing-the-yankee-players-continued-to-amaze-even-themselves-as-their-record-surge-carried-them-past-the-red-sox-and-into-first-place |magazine=Sports Illustrated |last=Keith |first=Larry |title=Seeing ain't believing |date=1978-09-25 |page=24 |access-date=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2020-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200828072008/https://vault.si.com/vault/1978/09/25/seeing-aint-believing-the-yankee-players-continued-to-amaze-even-themselves-as-their-record-surge-carried-them-past-the-red-sox-and-into-first-place }}</ref>；這讓洋基隊在僅剩三周時將戰績打平在86勝56敗（勝率：{{winning percentage|86|56|record=y}}）<ref name=hcianws>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=r-BGAAAAIBAJ&pg=3184%2C1783228 |work=The Day |location=(New London, Connecticut) |agency=Associated Press |title=Holy cow!! It's a new season |date=1978-09-11 |page=25 |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317093101/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=r-BGAAAAIBAJ&pg=3184%2C1783228 }}</ref><ref name=tdytrsox>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=v_lVAAAAIBAJ&pg=6573%2C3083438 |work=Eugene Register-Guard |location=Oregon |agency=wire service reports |title=Those Damn Yankees tie Red Sox for division lead |date=1978-09-11 |page=3B |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210617061814/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=v_lVAAAAIBAJ&pg=6573%2C3083438 }}</ref><ref name=tbgcol>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=HxNSAAAAIBAJ&pg=6838%2C2161995 |work=Nashua Telegraph |location=New Hampshire |agency=UPI |last=May |first=Peter |title=The Big Collapse: Part 4 is staged |date=1978-09-11 |page=31 |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210617061809/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=HxNSAAAAIBAJ&pg=6838%2C2161995 }}</ref>。

