===著名事件===
當年的衛冕軍在{{mlby|1978}}起步緩慢，迫使老闆[[喬治·史坦布瑞納|喬治·史坦布瑞納]]向總教練[[比利·馬丁|比利·馬丁]]施加更多壓力。馬丁與隊上球星[[瑞吉·傑克森_(棒球運動員)|瑞吉·傑克森]]之間的紛爭讓問題雪上加霜，史坦布瑞納同樣也因此事向馬丁施加壓力。7月17日，當時球隊以47勝42敗落居美聯東區第四，並來到{{le|1978年堪薩斯皇家隊球季|1978 Kansas City Royals season|堪薩斯皇家隊}}主場作客。雙方打到10局下半依然戰成5比5，此時首棒上來的[[瑟曼·蒙森|瑟曼·蒙森]]敲出一壘安打，接著總教練馬丁向傑克森下達[[犧牲觸擊|犧牲觸擊]]的戰術，但後者未能成功執行。於是馬丁又透過三壘教練{{le|狄克·豪瑟|Dick Howser}}向傑克森傳達改為揮棒的指令，雖然豪瑟成功轉達，但傑克森卻將其忽視並嘗試另一次觸擊。豪瑟叫出了暫停並與傑克森溝通，可仍無濟於事。在傑克森最後一次觸擊嘗試後，他擊出界外球遭到捕手接殺。馬丁因此將傑克森從場上移下，並給予後者禁賽處分（老闆史坦布瑞納將處分長度限縮到周二至周六五天），而皇家隊後來也在第十一局中勝出，於三連戰中橫掃了洋基隊。週二是輪空日，洋基隊前往{{le|1978年明尼蘇達雙城隊球季|1978 Minnesota Twins season|明尼蘇達}}，而傑克森則是飛往[[加州|加州]]<ref name=dyrjsus>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=WQsiAAAAIBAJ&pg=997%2C2864936 |work=The Day |location=New London, Connecticut |agency=Associated Press |title=Reggie Jackson suspended |date=1978-07-18 |page=19 |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210617061808/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=WQsiAAAAIBAJ&pg=997%2C2864936 }}</ref><ref name=ergbgoat>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=QMhYAAAAIBAJ&pg=3334%2C4963897 |work=Eugene Register-Guard |location=Oregon |agency=Associated Press |title=Billy's goat |date=1978-07-18 |page=1C |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317093026/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=QMhYAAAAIBAJ&pg=3334%2C4963897 }}</ref>。

傑克森於7月23日（日）在芝加哥歸隊，但他沒有參與打擊練習，也在洋基隊橫掃{{le|1978年芝加哥白襪隊球季|1978 Chicago White Sox season|白襪隊}}期間坐冷板凳，當時球隊還取得了五連勝<ref name=wmstur>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=J8ksAAAAIBAJ&pg=5750%2C4709796 |work=Wilmington Morning Star |location=North Carolina |agency=Associated Press |title=Yankees' turmoil |date=1978-07-24 |page=1C}}</ref>。馬丁在芝加哥機場舉行的賽後訪問提到：「一個生來就是騙子，另一個則是被定罪{{efn|one's a born liar, and the other's convicted.，暗指球星傑克森和老闆史坦布瑞納}}」。其中史坦布瑞納的部分，是暗示這位洋基隊老闆過去在美國總統大選中進行非法政治獻金。隔天馬丁在[[堪薩斯市|堪薩斯市]]的電視直播上，含淚宣布辭去洋基隊總教練一職<ref name=tmpest>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=LMksAAAAIBAJ&pg=6712%2C4782633 |work=Wilmington Morning Star |location=North Carolina |agency=''New York Times'' News Service |last=Cass |first=Murray |title=Tempestuous Martin out as manager |date=1978-07-25 |page=3B}}</ref><ref name=bshtrh>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=RshYAAAAIBAJ&pg=2240%2C6984799 |work=Eugene Register-Guard |location=Oregon |agency=wire service reports |title=Billy sheds a tear for himself |date=1978-07-25 |page=1D |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317093012/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=RshYAAAAIBAJ&pg=2240%2C6984799 }}</ref><ref name=mchasson>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=WwsiAAAAIBAJ&pg=4169%2C3924561 |work=The Day |location=New London, Connecticut |agency=New York Times |last=Chass |first=Murray |title=Billy Martin tearfully quits job with Yankees |date=1978-07-25 |page=1 |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317093010/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=WwsiAAAAIBAJ&pg=4169%2C3924561 }}</ref><ref name=odyend>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=D_ZLAAAAIBAJ&pg=6050%2C4025634 |work=Spokesman-Review |location=Spokane, Washington |agency=Associated Press |title=Odyssey ends: Billy quits |date=1978-07-25 |page=17 |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317093012/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=D_ZLAAAAIBAJ&pg=6050%2C4025634 }}</ref><ref name=abtwboom>{{cite magazine |url=https://vault.si.com/vault/1978/07/31/a-bunt-that-went-boom-for-bunting-when-manager-billy-martin-ordered-him-to-swing-away-reggie-jackson-was-suspended-and-so-began-a-chain-of-tumultuous-events-that-culminated-in-martins-resignation |magazine=Sports Illustrated |last=Keith |first=Larry |title=A bunt that went boom! |date=1978-07-31 |page=14 |access-date=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2020-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101101607/https://vault.si.com/vault/1978/07/31/a-bunt-that-went-boom-for-bunting-when-manager-billy-martin-ordered-him-to-swing-away-reggie-jackson-was-suspended-and-so-began-a-chain-of-tumultuous-events-that-culminated-in-martins-resignation }}</ref>，但多數來源相信他其實是因「指控定罪」的言論被史坦布瑞納給炒了<ref name=abtwboom/><ref name=remboss>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=WgsiAAAAIBAJ&pg=967%2C3843708 |work=The Day |location=New London, Connecticut |agency=Associated Press |title=Remarks about boss may bring Martin's dismissal |date=1978-07-24 |page=21}}</ref>。豪瑟隨後於7月24日對陣皇家隊的比賽中代行總教練一職，但他們這場由{{le|美國職棒大聯盟ABC轉播|Major League Baseball on ABC|ABC}}{{le|週一夜棒球|Monday Night Baseball}}轉播的對戰卻以2比5輸球，隨後[[鮑伯·雷蒙|鮑伯·雷蒙]]來到隊上接掌了剩餘賽季時的總教練兵符。

7月27日（四），在經歷觸擊事件後十天後，傑克森以右外野手身分重新出賽，並在當天打出三支三，包含一支全壘打、一次保送及三分打點。在雙重賽的夜場比賽，他又敲出兩支安打<ref name=yindsplt>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=NMksAAAAIBAJ&pg=5257%2C5399757 |work=Wilmington Morning Star |location=North Carolina |agency=Associated Press |title=Yankees, Indians split |date=1978-07-28 |page=3C}}</ref>。

7月29日（六）的老時光日典禮（Old-Timer's Day ceremony）在洋基球場舉行，洋基隊公眾廣播員[[鮑伯·謝帕德|鮑伯·謝帕德]]向大眾介紹了馬丁，並宣布馬丁將於{{le|1980年紐約洋基隊球季|1980 New York Yankees season|1980年球季}}重新擔任洋基隊總教練<ref name=mmygord>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=NsksAAAAIBAJ&pg=6629%2C5776391 |work=Sunday Star-News |location=Wilmington, North Carolina |agency=''New York Times'' News Service |last=Cass |first=Murray |title=Manager merry-go-round |date=1978-07-30 |page=1C}}</ref><ref name=nyrehbfe>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=DfUhAAAAIBAJ&pg=4692%2C5799714 |work=Reading Eagle |location=Pennsylvania |agency=Associated Press |title=New York rehires Billy for '80 |date=1978-07-30 |page=81}}</ref>。後來馬丁提前於{{le|1979年紐約洋基隊球季|1979 New York Yankees season|1979年}}6月重返洋基隊<ref name=msktsuc>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=s5hVAAAAIBAJ&pg=4138%2C5365366 |work=Reading Eagle |location=Pennsylvania |agency=Associated Press |title=Martin sees Jackson key to success |date=1979-06-19 |page=22}}</ref>，但僅四個月後，就因[[明尼蘇達|明尼蘇達]]旅館打架事件再次被炒魷魚<ref name=bmagn>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=1p8tAAAAIBAJ&pg=5812%2C6637978 |work=Reading Eagle |location=Pennsylvania |agency=Associated Press |last=Rappoport |first=Ken |title=Billy Martin axed again |date=1979-10-29 |page=22}}</ref><ref name=ppyfma>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=JmIdAAAAIBAJ&pg=3469%2C6221962 |work=Pittsburgh Press |agency=UPI |title=Yankees fire Martin again |date=1979-10-29 |page=B4}}</ref>。{{le|1980年奧克蘭運動家隊球季|1980 Oakland Athletics season|隔年}}他前往[[奧克蘭運動家隊|奧克蘭]]，擔綱{{le|查理·芬利|Charlie Finley}}控有的運動家隊總教練一職<ref name=mmghwaj>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=aTBPAAAAIBAJ&pg=7081%2C3466821 |work=Toledo Blade |location=Ohio |agency=Associated Press |title=Martin missed game, happy with A's job |date=1978-02-22 |page=21}}</ref><ref name=mbthto>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=0_tLAAAAIBAJ&pg=3195%2C3168156 |work=Spokesman-Review |location=Spokane, Washington |agency=Chicago Sun Times |title=Martin's back, thanks to Charlie O. |date=1980-02-22 |page=21}}</ref><ref name=bbchagn>{{cite magazine |url=https://vault.si.com/vault/1980/03/10/berkeley-billy-comes-home-again-born-in-the-bay-area-51-years-ago-billy-martin-is-back-in-the-neighborhood-as-manager-of-charlie-finleys-downtrodden-oakland-as-an-assignment-that-given-the-personalities-of-the-principals-may-not |magazine=Sports Illustrated |last=Fimrite |first=Ron |title=Berkeley Billy comes home again |date=1980-03-10 |page=18 |access-date=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304125248/https://vault.si.com/vault/1980/03/10/berkeley-billy-comes-home-again-born-in-the-bay-area-51-years-ago-billy-martin-is-back-in-the-neighborhood-as-manager-of-charlie-finleys-downtrodden-oakland-as-an-assignment-that-given-the-personalities-of-the-principals-may-not }}</ref>。之後馬丁又於{{le|1983年紐約洋基隊球季|1983 New York Yankees season|1983年}}、{{le|1985年紐約洋基隊球季|1985 New York Yankees season|1985年}}、{{le|1988年紐約洋基隊球季|1988 New York Yankees season|1988年}}回鍋洋基隊擔任總教練。

洋基隊在雷蒙執教下的1978年剩餘球季中共獲得47勝20敗，從7月19日落後十四場勝差的窘境，一路追平分區第一的戰績。後來他們更是在一場定生死的[[1978年美國聯盟東區封王決勝加賽|客場決勝加賽]]中勝出<ref name=ywpogth/><ref name=yedbsxptn/><ref name=ydrsprfp/>，並最終在[[1978年世界大賽|世界大賽]]中連霸。

9月30日，{{le|艾德·菲格羅亞|Ed Figueroa}}拿下本季第20勝，助隊並列美聯第一<ref name=clntie>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=TesyAAAAIBAJ&pg=6924%2C147484 |work=Sunday Star-News |location=Wilmington, North Carolina |agency=Associated Press |title=Yanks clinch AL East tie, but Boston wins, too |date=1978-10-01 |page=5C}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=nw7MDAAAQBAJ&q=ed+figueroa+20th+win+1978&pg=PA108|title=Chronology of Latin Americans in Baseball, 1871-2015|first=Lou|last=HernÌÁndez|date=2016-06-27|publisher=McFarland|isbn=9781476662275|via=Google Books}}</ref>。而菲格羅雅也是截至2018年止，唯一一位能在大聯盟單季20勝的土生土長[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sabr.org/bioproj/person/750a1e46|title=Ed Figueroa - Society for American Baseball Research|website=sabr.org|access-date=2021-03-01|archive-date=2020-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200206031822/https://sabr.org/bioproj/person/750a1e46}}</ref>。

